Interface ConfiguredMaster

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    _MPMCompatibleMaster, _MPMConsumableResourceMaster, _MPMMfgStandardGroupedMaster, _MPMOperationHolderMaster, _MPMQualityHolderMaster, MPMCompatibleMaster, MPMConsumableResourceMaster, MPMMfgStandardGroupedMaster, MPMOperationHolderMaster, MPMQualityHolderMaster
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    _MPMControlCharacteristicMaster, _MPMMfgProcessMaster, _MPMMfgStandardGroupMaster, _MPMOperationMaster, _MPMProcessMaterialMaster, _MPMProcessPlanMaster, _MPMSequenceMaster, _MPMSkillMaster, _MPMToolingMaster, _PartListMaster, MPMControlCharacteristicMaster, MPMMfgProcessMaster, MPMMfgStandardGroupMaster, MPMOperationMaster, MPMProcessMaterialMaster, MPMProcessPlanMaster, MPMSequenceMaster, MPMSkillMaster, MPMToolingMaster, PartListMaster

    @GenAsPersistable(interfaces=Mastered.class,
                  extendable=true)
public interface ConfiguredMaster
    A configured object is a versioned object that is structured in some manner for which configurations that represent its structure can be stored.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
    See Also:
    ConfiguredVersion, BaselineConfigurationMaster, WTPartMaster
